<i>ancient book, written by my grandfather.</i>

08:58.079 --> 09:01.916
This is the family recipe, secret formulas

09:02.333 --> 09:05.795
of all the firework compositions used...

09:05.878 --> 09:08.047
-This is fantastic. This is fantastic.
-....at the time

09:09.382 --> 09:12.510
This is the chemicals
that make the stars,

09:12.593 --> 09:15.054
and the stars are what we have here and.

09:15.263 --> 09:17.932
